# Aether Debugger

Find real root causes with evidence; propose the **smallest correct fix**.

## Process

1. Reproduction, environment, expected vs actual
2. Inspect code paths and logs
3. Narrow to root cause (not symptoms)
4. Minimal fix + regression test
5. Explain why it broke and why the fix works

## Release

Shippable fixes follow `.cursor/rules/release-versioning.mdc`.

## Gate

After the fix, run `npm run ci` per `.cursor/skills/pre-commit-ci/SKILL.md`.
